The hidden costs that impact multi-location operators:

<strong>Carrier fees:</strong> $0.0025-0.004 per message on top of stated rates for carrier surcharges. These fluctuate and are passed through at cost.

<strong>Toll-free verification:</strong> Free, but takes 2-3 weeks. Budget time before major campaigns.

<strong>10DLC registration:</strong> Required for campaign-scale sending. $15 one-time fee per brand, $1/month per campaign. If you're operating separate Shopify stores per location, this adds up.

<strong>Short code:</strong> Optional dedicated short codes cost $1,500+/month but significantly improve deliverability and brand recognition. Worth it above 100,000 subscribers in our experience.

For context, our 412,000-subscriber operation across 47 locations costs approximately $18,500/month all-in. That breaks down to roughly $393 per location per month, generating an average of $4,200 in SMS-attributed revenue per location. The unit economics work, but only because we've optimized relentlessly.

